ventmenu - dynamic menu based on dmenu 5.0
====================
ventmenu is a heavily patched version of dmenu 5.0 which itself is an efficient dynamic menu for X.

Differences
-----------
- Applied center patch to center dmenu without the need to use a bash / sh script.


Requirements
------------
In order to build ventmenu you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (ventmenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install ventmenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running ventmenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
